    "attributes": {
        "action": "Limit yearly council tax increases to level of inflation",
        "additional_details": "This has put enormous strain on normal families to cover the rise. Thus, council tax should not be allowed to rise more than inflation.",
        "background": "Many local authorities are increasing their levels of council tax at unprecedented rates. 116 out of 151 councils have increased the council tax bill to the maximum 3.99%, outstripping the rise in inflation.",
